name: CoraJadeV1 Textual Inversion
description:
Hey there, this is my first ti. It recreates images of wrestler Cora Jade. The idea to create this ti came from a friend who asked me to generate pictures of her in SD but without the ti I couldn't get decent images. The first few tries where a total disaster and I didn't touch the files in much. But thanks to JernauGurgeh and his help I was able to get the process done. So many thanks to them! Most of the prompts show here to generate the images are basically theirs too. :D

Any feedback is welcome!

Feel free to leave me a tip/buy me a coffee if you like what I am doing :)
